gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Grizzlies 116, Warriors 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Grizzlies defeated the Warriors, 116-107. Vince Williams Jr. recorded a career-high 24 points, along with seven rebounds and four assists for the Grizzlies, while GG Jackson added a career-high 23 points and five 3PM in the victory. Stephen Curry tallied 26 points and eight assists for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Grizzlies improve to 15-25 on the season, while the Warriors fall to 18-22.
